<u>Ha</u>meem
Wa<b>a</b>lkit<u>a</u>bi almubeen<b>i</b>
Inn<u>a</u> anzaln<u>a</u>hu fee laylatin mub<u>a</u>rakatin inn<u>a</u> kunn<u>a</u> mun<u>th</u>ireen<b>a</b>
Feeh<u>a</u> yufraqu kullu amrin <u>h</u>akeem<b>in</b>
Amran min AAindin<u>a</u> inn<u>a</u> kunn<u>a</u> mursileen<b>a</b>
Ra<u>h</u>matan min rabbika innahu huwa a<b>l</b>ssameeAAu alAAaleem<b>u</b>
Rabbi a<b>l</b>ssam<u>a</u>w<u>a</u>ti wa<b>a</b>lar<u>d</u>i wam<u>a</u> baynahum<u>a</u> in kuntum mooqineen<b>a</b>
L<u>a</u> il<u>a</u>ha ill<u>a</u> huwa yu<u>h</u>yee wayumeetu rabbukum warabbu <u>a</u>b<u>a</u>ikumu alawwaleen<b>a</b>
Bal hum fee shakkin yalAAaboon<b>a</b>
Fa<b>i</b>rtaqib yawma tatee a<b>l</b>ssam<u>a</u>o bidukh<u>a</u>nin mubeen<b>in</b>
Yaghsh<u>a</u> a<b>l</b>nn<u>a</u>sa h<u>atha</u> AAa<u>tha</u>bun aleem<b>un</b>
Rabban<u>a</u> ikshif AAann<u>a</u> alAAa<u>tha</u>ba inn<u>a</u> muminoon<b>a</b>
Ann<u>a</u> lahumu a<b>l</b><u>thth</u>ikr<u>a</u> waqad j<u>a</u>ahum rasoolun mubeen<b>un</b>
Thumma tawallaw AAanhu waq<u>a</u>loo muAAallamun majnoon<b>un</b>
Inn<u>a</u> k<u>a</u>shifoo alAAa<u>tha</u>bi qaleelan innakum AA<u>a</u>idoon<b>a</b>
Yawma nab<u>t</u>ishu alba<u>t</u>shata alkubr<u>a</u> inn<u>a</u> muntaqimoon<b>a</b>
Walaqad fatann<u>a</u> qablahum qawma firAAawna waj<u>a</u>ahum rasoolun kareem<b>un</b>
An addoo ilayya AAib<u>a</u>da All<u>a</u>hi innee lakum rasoolun ameen<b>un</b>
Waan l<u>a</u> taAAloo AAal<u>a</u> All<u>a</u>hi innee <u>a</u>teekum bisul<u>ta</u>nin mubeen<b>in</b>
Wainnee AAu<u>th</u>tu birabbee warabbikum an tarjumoon<b>i</b>
Wain lam tuminoo lee fa<b>i</b>AAtaziloon<b>i</b>
FadaAA<u>a</u> rabbahu anna h<u>a</u>ol<u>a</u>i qawmun mujrimoon<b>a</b>
Faasri biAAib<u>a</u>dee laylan innakum muttabaAAoon<b>a</b>
Wa<b>o</b>truki alba<u>h</u>ra rahwan innahum jundun mughraqoon<b>a</b>
Kam tarakoo min jann<u>a</u>tin waAAuyoon<b>in</b>
WazurooAAin wamaq<u>a</u>min kareem<b>in</b>
WanaAAmatin k<u>a</u>noo feeh<u>a</u> f<u>a</u>kiheen<b>a</b>
Ka<u>tha</u>lika waawrathn<u>a</u>h<u>a</u> qawman <u>a</u>khareen<b>a</b>
Fam<u>a</u> bakat AAalayhimu a<b>l</b>ssam<u>a</u>o wa<b>a</b>lar<u>d</u>u wam<u>a</u> k<u>a</u>noo mun<i><u>th</u></i>areen<b>a</b>
Walaqad najjayn<u>a</u> banee isr<u>a</u>eela mina alAAa<u>tha</u>bi almuheen<b>i</b>
Min firAAawna innahu k<u>a</u>na AA<u>a</u>liyan mina almusrifeen<b>a</b>
Walaqadi ikhtarn<u>a</u>hum AAal<u>a</u> AAilmin AAal<u>a</u> alAA<u>a</u>lameen<b>a</b>
Wa<u>a</u>tayn<u>a</u>hum mina al<u>a</u>y<u>a</u>ti m<u>a</u> feehi bal<u>a</u>on mubeen<b>un</b>
Inna h<u>a</u>ol<u>a</u>i layaqooloon<b>a</b>
In hiya ill<u>a</u> mawtatun<u>a</u> alool<u>a</u> wam<u>a</u> na<u>h</u>nu bimunshareen<b>a</b>
Fatoo bi<u>a</u>b<u>a</u>in<u>a</u> in kuntum <u>sa</u>diqeen<b>a</b>
Ahum khayrun am qawmu tubbaAAin wa<b>a</b>lla<u>th</u>eena min qablihim ahlakn<u>a</u>hum innahum k<u>a</u>noo mujrimeen<b>a</b>
Wam<u>a</u> khalaqn<u>a</u> a<b>l</b>ssam<u>a</u>w<u>a</u>ti wa<b>a</b>lar<u>d</u>a wam<u>a</u> baynahum<u>a</u> l<u>a</u>AAibeen<b>a</b>
M<u>a</u> khalaqn<u>a</u>hum<u>a</u> ill<u>a</u> bi<b>a</b>l<u>h</u>aqqi wal<u>a</u>kinna aktharahum l<u>a</u> yaAAlamoon<b>a</b>
Inna yawma alfa<u>s</u>li meeq<u>a</u>tuhum ajmaAAeen<b>a</b>
Yawma l<u>a</u> yughnee mawlan AAan mawlan shayan wal<u>a</u> hum yun<u>s</u>aroon<b>a</b>
Ill<u>a</u> man ra<u>h</u>ima All<u>a</u>hu innahu huwa alAAazeezu a<b>l</b>rra<u>h</u>eem<b>u</b>
Inna shajarata a<b>l</b>zzaqqoom<b>i</b>
<u>T</u>aAA<u>a</u>mu alatheem<b>i</b>
Ka<b>a</b>lmuhli yaghlee fee albu<u>t</u>oon<b>i</b>
Kaghalyi al<u>h</u>ameem<b>i</b>
Khu<u>th</u>oohu fa<b>i</b>AAtiloohu il<u>a</u> saw<u>a</u>i alja<u>h</u>eem<b>i</b>
Thumma <u>s</u>ubboo fawqa rasihi min AAa<u>tha</u>bi al<u>h</u>ameem<b>i</b>
<u>Th</u>uq innaka anta alAAazeezu alkareem<b>u</b>
Inna h<u>atha</u> m<u>a</u> kuntum bihi tamtaroon<b>a</b>
Inna almuttaqeena fee maq<u>a</u>min ameen<b>in</b>
Fee jann<u>a</u>tin waAAuyoon<b>in</b>
Yalbasoona min sundusin waistabraqin mutaq<u>a</u>bileen<b>a</b>
Ka<u>tha</u>lika wazawwajn<u>a</u>hum bi<u>h</u>oorin AAeen<b>in</b>
YadAAoona feeh<u>a</u> bikulli f<u>a</u>kihatin <u>a</u>mineen<b>a</b>
L<u>a</u> ya<u>th</u>ooqoona feeh<u>a</u> almawta ill<u>a</u> almawtata alool<u>a</u> wawaq<u>a</u>hum AAa<u>tha</u>ba alja<u>h</u>eem<b>i</b>
Fa<u>d</u>lan min rabbika <u>tha</u>lika huwa alfawzu alAAa<i><u>th</u></i>eem<b>u</b>
Fainnam<u>a</u> yassarn<u>a</u>hu bilis<u>a</u>nika laAAallahum yata<u>th</u>akkaroon<b>a</b>
Fa<b>i</b>rtaqib innahum murtaqiboon<b>a</b>
